=======================================================
[USEAGE]
python3 tracrRNA_analysis_SE.py pathfile [single-end]
python3 tracrRNA_analysis_PE.py pathfile [paired-end]
======================================================
pathfile
[single-end]
sample_1_name:read
sample_2_name:read
sample_3_name:read
......
[paired-end]
sample_1_name:read1:read2
sample_2_name:read1:read2
sample_3_name:read1:read2
......
======================================================
Attention: read file must be absolute path! eg./home/scx/crispr/CL0239109301_L01_54.fq.gz
